    "It uses a transformer encoder-based architecture to calculate word embedding.",
    "Although compared with the BiLSTM model on the transmission encoder, BERT is a powerful feature extractor.",
    "But in a larger corpus, BERT has longer training and inference time.",
    "It also contains large memory requirements.",
    "By designing a fine-tuned BERT model for future research, these practical problems can be alleviated."
